🌲It's ALMOST HERE! 🌲
Our last market of the year and it's with a few of my most favorite people!

JOIN US on THIS Sunday, December 18 from 10am - 4pm at @align.space for West Chester's first Handmade Holiday featuring the art and craft of 12 local artists. Peruse beautiful gifts for your loved ones, enjoy special holiday treats, and visit with our special guest before stepping out and enjoying the streets of West Chester at the holidays.

In need of any last-minute holiday gifts? Make a day of it and bring the kids!

🌱🌱I'll be there with paperwhites, amaryllis...regular and waxed! Bulbs bagged and potted up! Kits for gifting. Dried flower ornaments. Lavender trees. Frosty ferns. Handmade winter gardens for gifting. Everlasting dried flower wreaths and other fun goodies too!

align.Space is located at
2 W. Market St.
West Chester, PA 19382

Check out this amazing list of vendors below that I'll be spending the day with! ❤️ We hope to see you there! Do us a favor and spread the word by sharing this first annual market with your local friends! 🙏🏼

